      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was prescribed diazepam to help me sleep because i havent been sleeping well lately... i was wondering if it's okay to have like a small glass of red wine with it? i feel like it might actually help me drift off faster if i combine them? is that safe for just a little bit?",
