    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle lol. just like a single glass of wine to take the edge off. i feel like the wine would just help the diazepam work more effectively so i can actually stay asleep. i feel like if i'm careful with the amount, it shouldn't be a big deal, right? wouldn't the relaxing effect just be slightly stronger?",
