      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i understand the theory, but i've seen people do this before without any issues. if i just take a tiny bit less of the diazepam so it balances out with the wine, wouldn't that make it even safer? like i just want to know if the combination itself is actually a huge medical emergency or if it's just something doctors say to be overly cautious. can't i just manage the dose myself to make it work?",
